facsimile copy on canvas of Hatke's oil portrait of Christina (2007.1 UCPC); there is a slight sheen, almost glittery effect on the surface of this facsimile; also, this print is more yellow-orange than the painting; half-length, full face portrait of the subject; according to a typed note in the vertical file folder, she is wearing an academic robe from Brown University; behind her is a near life-size rendition of a frieze from the Parthenon, "Two Riders in the Procession at the Great Panathenaic Festival"

